      "side": 1,
      "message": "I realize that you are going to add several new plugins for notification methods, but some of these will still be \"relatively\" well known, such as HIPCHAT, SLACK and JIRA. I think in all of these cases if the period !\u003d 0, then it should throw an exception, as I think that is the behaviour that we want. Additionally, you could add validation logic for these if there is some validation that you want to do on the address.",
